      <title>多项调查驳斥了特朗普关于欺诈改变了 2020 年结果的说法</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/16/us/politics/trump-investigations-fraud-claims-2020-election.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数十项调查、审计、重新计票和法庭程序对 2020 年选举进行了审查。没有人发现特朗普总统声称的普遍选民欺诈导致选票倾斜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/16/us/politics/trump-investigations-fraud-claims-2020-election.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 01:03:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
